snippet.title: 🎋 Bamboo Helped Her Survive! 🔥💪 #camping #survival #bushcraft #outdoors #lifehack
snippet.description:
Making fire with bamboo is a time-tested survival skill — and yes, it still works!

Here’s what you need to know:
✔ Use hard, dry bamboo — yellow or slightly green is best.
❌ Avoid gray bamboo — it’s been waterlogged and wears out too fast.
✔ A bit damp? Just dry it in the sun or wipe it down.
✔ Start rubbing slowly — it helps warm the surface and push out moisture.
✔ Sharper edges = better friction.
✔ Save your energy — once you smell burning, that’s your cue to speed up and press harder.
✔ Smoke doesn’t mean fire yet — keep going!
⚠️ Don’t forget to prepare a tinder nest in advance — once the ember forms, gently place it inside to blow it into flame.

For this process I used my ROXON S803E Elite multitool — super handy in the wild!
🛠️ Link in bio if you’re curious.

I did it — and so can you! 💪🔥

The 2nd leg of MPL PH Season 15 is here & every win counts. Teams are fighting their slot to be the best in the League.
The week will start with a game between Twisted Minds PH & Aurora Gaming. TWIS are starting to look good with their own definition of the meta while Aurora wants to maintain themselves as the team to beat after going invinsible in the first 7 games.
The next game will see a star studden line up of World Champions Onic Philippines in a red-hot 3 games win streak going up against TNC Pro Team who has looked like a title contender with the addition of BennyQT.

Match Schedule, first match starts at 5PM:
⚔️ TWIS vs. RORA
⚔️ ONIC vs. TNC

See you in the Land of Dawn!

snippet.title: Kasalan, naudlot dahil si groom, ginayuma diumano ni bride? | Kapuso Mo, Jessica Soho
snippet.description:
Aired (March 16, 2025):

KASALAN SA CAGAYAN DE ORO CITY, NAUDLOT DAHIL SI GROOM, GINAYUMA DIUMANO NI BRIDE? 

Paalala: Maging disente sa mga komento.

Simple pero elegante ang set up ng civil wedding sa Cagayan de Oro City sa Mindanao. Pero ang groom, biglang nag-backout?!

Ang lalaking dapat ikakasal, ginayuma lang diumano ng babae!

Natauhan lang daw ang groom, matapos itong sabuyan… ng asin!

Ano nga ba ang totoo sa mga kumalat na kuwento? 

Panoorin ang video. #KMJS
